<P>
   GAYS-CONSERVATIVES (Washington) _ Gay rights groups charge that
the religious right is using the argument that homosexuals can
become heterosexual through Christianity to block antibias laws. We
get reaction from one of the groups' targets, the Family Research
Council. By ERIC ROSENBERG.
