<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1998-10-15 15:13 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A8965 &Cx1f; tdt-z
u a &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-FEATURE-BUDGET-ART-BO     10-15 0465
