</P>
<P>
   &UR; NEW YORK TIMES THIRD-QUARTER MUTUAL FUND REPORT &LR;
</P>
<P>
   MUTFUND-OVERVIEW-NYT (Undated) _ Lessons of the selloffs. By
Edward Wyatt. With Graphic.
</P>
<P>
   MUTFUND-BONDS-NYT (Undated) _ Why bond funds fail. By Gretchen
