Toombs is the key to the Aggies bid for a Big 12 championship.
(Riggs, Austin American-Statesman).
</P>
<P>
   FBC-WANGRIN _ The Texas defense has come a long ways from the
season opener against New Mexico State and the routs at UCLA and
Kansas State. (Wangrin Austin American-Statesman).
</P>
